title: sic transit gloria mundi
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2Th9g3e

by rapmonied

“Thus passes the glory of the world”;

The world who is rotten and has no morals has no glory, either. Or at least, that was the world of Kim Namjoon and his people, a dangerous and addicting world that will never let you go once it’s sucked you in. It’s also the world completely opposite to the world Yoongi lives to protect. When both of these worlds are threatened Namjoon and Yoongi have no choice but to put aside their differences and work together.

title: S c e n t e d •제1장•
body:
⇢ pairing | jungkook/character
⇢ word c | 538
⇢ genre | soulmate au,angsty
⇢ summary |she met him,everything change.

⇢ warnings/tags |  possessiveness, enemies to lovers, jealousy, dirty talk,mental and physical abuse,violence

Peoples that seems to crowd the hallway annoyed me the most as it’s the peek hour now.

Recess time.

I pluck my earphones,playing some music and shove my hands into my black baggy hoodie pockets,walking straight to the spot where i used to distance myself from the crowd, probably every human beings around me.I hate to socialise.So dont try to make me interact with people.

I sit under a shady tree that located not so far away from the school building.And again,disappearing from the reality whenever im thinking what would happen to my life.

“i just wish that i would just disappear from this effing world..”

“why is it so hard to even breath..”

“mom should just killed me back then.."with teary eyes i buried my face to both of my hands.

"hey miss?are you okay?” a vaguely familiar,deep,throaty and husky voice that make me flinch by the sudden greet but yeah ofcourse stay cool heeyoung.

“mind your fcking business,you jerk.” i quickly stand up and ready to walk away but that guy suddenly grab my arm.

“tsk,have some manner princess.” he smirk and i just roll my eyes,yanking my arm to free myself from him.

“get loss”

Totally that jerk really have the urge to get on my nerve.But wait a second..

I quickly turned my heels and saw him,grinning like an idiot to me.

“do i know you?"i asked repositioning myself to his direction.

"do you should know me?” he crossed his arms while lifting his right eyebrow.

“nevermind.” maybe im wrong?but how come?

That voice.That smile.That eyes.Everything on him really looks familiar to..

No,enough is enough heeyoung.Forget about him wont you?

“she’s god damn beautiful..” jungkook mumble as his eyes still following the girl figure.

“wtf did i just fucking say?!oh my stop it jungkook..” jungkook slightly covered his mouth,not believing the words that came out from his mouth.

Recess time just ended.All students just casually walk to their own classes.I walk to my next class,it is math class which means my most hated subject.

“i dont know what happen to her life,but look at her beautiful face.it such a waste,she could be a really hot girl if she didn’t avoid people.” one of girl spoke up when she see heeyoung passby a group of girls.The others girl just nod agreeing the statement.

heeyoung totally spaced out from the class as she turned her head to the window beside her.

“erm,excuse me,is this Mrs.Lee’s class?” the whole class abruptly began to fill with murmured when a dark brown haired boy knocked the door class.

“woah,is that jeon jungkook?”

“im sure he is jeon jungkook,one of bts member”

“oh my,kookie!”

Jungkook just smiled and slightly bowed to the class.Of course he will be well recognise since BTS had become the most popular boy group nowadays.

“yes,just come in and take a sit please.” Mrs.Lee smiled,continuing her work.

Jungkook’s smile never fade when he is walking to the back of the class,taking his place next to a girl that constantly looking outside,not bother to spare him a glance.

“hi?” he greet the girl but she just remain silent.

“erm,hello there?"still not giving up to get her attention.

Finally their eyes met,making both of them gasped.

"seriously,you again?”
